est son. It was borne also by three kings of Scotland, notably  Robert the Bruce  (  1274–1329 ), who freed Scotland from English domination. The altered short form <i>Bob</i> is very common, but <i>Hob</i> and <i>Dob</i>, which were common in the Middle Ages and gave rise to surnames, are extinct.  See also  Rupert ."],"variants":[]}],"lifeSummary":"Robert de Essex married Alice before 1136, in Europe. They were the parents of at least 1 daughter."},"et":{"–":"Surnud","–Female":"Surnud","1136–Female":"1136–Surnud","–Male":"Surnud","before 1136":"enne 1136","1136":"1136","Europe":"Europe","Warkworth, Northumberland, England":"Warkworth, Northumberland, England"},"fi":{"–":"Kuollut","–Female":"Kuollut","1136–Female":"1136–Kuollut","–Male":"Kuollut","before 1136":"ennen vuotta 1136","1136":"1136","Europe":"Europe","Warkworth, Northumberland, England":"Warkworth, Northumberland, England"},"fr":{"–":"Décédé","–Female":"Décédée","1136–Female":"1136–Décédée","–Male":"Décédé","before 1136":"avant 1136","1136":"1136","Europe":"Europe","Warkworth, Northumberland, England":"Warkworth, Northumberland, Angleterre","lifeSummary":"Robert d’Essex a épousé Alice avant 1136, à Europe. Ils ont eu au moins 1 fille."},"de":{"–":"Verstorben","–Female":"Verstorben","1136–Female":"1136–Verstorben","–Male":"Verstorben","before 1136":"vor 1136","1136":"1136","Europe":"Europa","Warkworth, Northumberland, England":"Warkworth, Northumberland, England","lifeSummary":"Robert de Essex hat vor 1136 in Europa Alice geheiratet. Sie hatten mindestens 1 Tochter."},"ht":{"–":"Desede","–Female":"Desede","1136–Female":"1136–Desede","–Male":"Desede","before 1136":"before 1136","1136":"1136","Europe":"Europe","Warkworth, Northumberland, England":"Warkworth, Northumberland, England"},"hu":{"–":"elhunyt","–Female":"elhunyt","1136–Female":"1136–elhunyt","–Male":"elhunyt","before 1136":"1136 előtt","1136":"1136","Europe":"Europe","Warkworth, Northumberland, England":"Warkworth, Northumberland, England"},"id":{